file.name: getResources.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Example API
paths:
  '/v1/resources':
    get:
      description: Get a list of resources
      operationId: getResources
      security:
        - BasicAuth: [ ]
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/FilterById'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/FilterByName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/FilterByIds'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/ResourceFilter'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: list of resources
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Resource'
        '400':
          description: Invalid request parameters.
  '/v1/resources/sub-resources':
    get:
      description: Get a list of sub resources
      operationId: getSubResources
      security:
          - BearerAuth: []
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/SubResourceFilter'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: list of resources
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Resource'
        '400':
          description: Invalid request parameters.
components:
  securitySchemes:
    BearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT
    BasicAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: basic
  schemas:
    Resource:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
  parameters:
    FilterById:
      name: filterById
      in: query
      schema:
        type: integer
    FilterByName:
      name: filterByName
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
    FilterByIds:
      name: filterByIds
      in: query
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          type: integer
    ResourceFilter:
      name: filter
      in: query
      schema:
        type: object
        properties:
          prop1:
            type: string
    SubResourceFilter:
      name: filter
      in: query
      schema:
        type: object
        properties:
          prop1:
            type: integer
